high_descs: Turn to your left, walk towards the door then turn left
Open the door of the cabinet and pick up the pan inside
Turn to your left and head on the fridge
Open the fridge, put the pan inside the fridge then close the door
Open the fridge then get the pan inside and close the door. Turn around and head to the stove
Put the pan on the left top side of the stove
anns.task_desc: Put the pan on the stove

high_descs: turn left and walk to the end of the room, then turn left and walk to the counter corner
grab a sauce pan out of the cabinet below the kitchen corner counter
turn around and walk to the fridge at the end of the room on the right
place the sauce pan inside of the fridge, close the door, let it cool and take it out, then close the door again
turn around and walk to kitchen counter, then turn right and walk to the stove
place the pan on the back left burner of the stovetop
anns.task_desc: place a cooled pan on the kitchen stovetop

high_descs: Turn left, cross the room and hang a left at the white door to reach the counter.
Open the lower far right cabinet, pick up the black pan from inside and close the door.
Turn around and cross the room to reach the black fridge.
Put the black pan inside the fridge in the middle of the wire shelf, close the door, let it chill for seven seconds, remove it from the fridge and close the door.
Turn around and hang a right at the counter to face the stove.
Put the pan on the far left burner of the stove top.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled pan on the stove.
